          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer113681253" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7040490155636300137">Wish I had read this in 2004 when it was published, but it is still relevant today. I reread the last chapter three times -- it is just that brilliant. Reich says there is no such thing as a moderate Democrat, if a Democrat moves to the center it is because they are looking for more lobby money.<br/><br/>This is a must read for anyone who cares about America. <br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


